# Job-Seeker-SAAS
Job Seeker is a AI powered software through which finding your dream jobs becomes a lot less hectic and easy.
It is python based web application where the user
> User will registter itself with the platform 
> After Succesful registration the user needs to login in to the application 
>The application will demand a prompt on an instruction
>This instruction can llok like 'ML engineer in vienna'
> then the application will use a real time web scrapping tool Brightdata to find teh jobs that suit you
> the application brings you the jobs you want

# Technologies Used 
To develop this application we have used 
[![DJANGO](data:image/png;base64,)](https://www.djangoproject.com/):Django used for the web framework 
[![LANGCHAIN](data:image/jpeg;base64,)](https://www.langchain.com/) For Natural Language Processing
[![CELERY](data:image/png;base64,)](https://docs.celeryq.dev/en/main/getting-started/introduction.html) Celery for task distribution 
[![REDIS](data:image/png;base64,)](https://redis.io/) Redis for caching and storing the snapshot and the resultant job listings
[![DOCKER](data:image/png;base64,)](https://www.docker.com/) Docker for containerisation 
[![UV](data:image/png;base64,)](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/guides/install-python/) UV a rust based python package installer for high speed installation.
